<html>
<head>
<title>Text Formatting</title>
</head>
<body>
<h1>My First Page</h1>
<p>This is a normal paragraph.</p>
<b>This text is bold</b><br>
<i>This text is italic</i><br>
<u>This text is underlined</u><br>
<big>This is big text</big><br>
<small>This is small text</small><br>
<strong>This is important</strong><br>
<em>This is emphasized</em><br>
<mark>This is highlighted</mark><br>
<del>This is deleted</del><br>
H<sub>2</sub>O is water<br>
X<sup>2</sup> is x squared
</body>
</html>
